<h2>Basic Example</h2>

<p>This example will show how this component can retrieve the set of fields values and convert them into javascript object literal, also the load button will refill the fields after save and then reset button is clicked. </p>
<p>If save button is clicked, the object result can be seen and how the fields are retrieved.</p>

